<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hello, <%= @payment.email %>.  This is PayMonkey, your friendly neighborhood loan shark :)</h1>
    <p>
      You owe some money to a friend, who wants to be paid back.<br/>
      Payment description: <%= @payment.description %><br/>
      Payment amount:  <%= @payment.amount %><br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      We'll send you reminders so you don't forget.<br/>
      Once you have paid back your friend, follow this link to confirm and 
        stop receiving these reminders: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
